cs.HC, cs.MM, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.GR 

The paper discusses a multimodal game with a purpose that leverages on the wisdom of crowds phenomenon for the annotation of multimedia data in terms of mental states. This involves aspects of human-computer interaction (cs.HC), multimedia (cs.MM), natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and graphics (cs.GR). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.HC and cs.MM, followed by cs.CL, cs.AI, and cs.GR.
